Dude, name a babe, all right?
Any babe in Seattle.

1138
01:11:37,334 --> 01:11:40,128
I'll set you up with her.
♪ He's not sure
what to do ♪

1139
01:11:40,212 --> 01:11:43,881
Diane Court!
Dude, I can't do it, buddy.

1140
01:11:43,966 --> 01:11:47,260
